content.html: Today I finally made the frontend for a project I did 80% of back in July. It's ima.ge.cx and it's a way to browse the contents of Docker images without needing to pull them to your computer. It works but has a bunch of bugs because I am not a full-stack dev. 1/5
content.value:
Today I finally made the frontend for a project I did 80% of back in July. It's ima.ge.cx and it's a way to browse the contents of Docker images without needing to pull them to your computer.

It works but has a bunch of bugs because I am not a full-stack dev.

1/5
